metadata.Plot: Kisha and Rob are the picture perfect couple, but even perfect people have secrets. When Nicole, an old friend, comes into town with her new man, Kisha and Rob's world is turned upside down. While catching up over drinks. Kisha admits that she is no longer satisfied in the bedroom. And Nicole takes that as an invitation to help Kisha and Rob spice things up. During a night of fun and games, Nicole suggests that they swap partners. However, all is not what it may seem, and after their night of passion, the couples begin down a path that changed all of their lives forever.
